\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u1ec3 ho\xe0n t\u1ea5t giao d\u1ecbch.","line2":"B\u1ea1n vui l\xf2ng \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ecdc gi\u1eef xe \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng x\xe1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01a1n h\xe0ng.","note2":"\u0110\u1ec3 ho\xe0n t\u1ea5t quy tr\xecnh thu\xea xe, Chungxe c\u1ea7n th\u1ea9m \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Xin vui l\xf2ng cung c\u1ea5p \u1ea3nh ch\u1ee5p gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n theo y\xeau c\u1ea7u d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\xe2y:","note3":"C\u1ea3m \u01a1n b\u1ea1n \u0111\xe3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ChungXe !","note_create_acc":"Ch\xfang t\xf4i \u0111\xe3 t\u1ea1o cho b\u1ea1n 1 t\xe0i kho\u1ea3n. Vui l\xf2ng ki\u1ec3m tra email \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y th\xf4ng tin \u0111\u0103ng nh\u1eadp."},"book_code":"M\xe3 \u0111\u1eb7t xe c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n:","btn_home":"V\u1ec1 trang ch\u1ee7","btn_info":"Upload h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 c\xe1 nh\xe2n","btn_deposit":"\u0110\u1eb7t c\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o","btn_payment":"Thanh to\xe1n ti\u1ec1n thu\xea xe","btn_cancel":"H\u1ee7y \u0111\u1eb7t xe","book_status":"Xe \u0111\xe3 s\u1eb5n s\xe0ng","book_status_receive":"\u0110\xe3 gi\u1eef xe","book_status_processing":"\u0110ang x\u1eed l\xfd","book_status_ready":"Xe \u0111\xe3 s\u1eb5n s\xe0ng","add_to_gg_calendar":"Th\xeam v\xe0o l\u1ecbch Google","add_to_ical_calendar":"Th\xeam v\xe0o l\u1ecbch iCal/Outlook","note-content1":"\u0110\u0103ng t\u1ea3i h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 thu\xea xe gi\xfap qu\xe1 tr\xecnh thu\xea xe nhanh v\xe0 ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n.","note-content2":"Chungxe t\u1eb7ng b\u1ea1n m\xe3 50000 vn\u0111 n\u1ebfu ho\xe0n t\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i","note-content3":"\u0110\u1eb7t c\u1ecdc nhanh \u0111\u1ec3 ho\xe0n th\xe0nh vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef xe","note-content4":"C\xf3 {{count}} ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\xe1c \u0111ang xem xe n\xe0y","note-content5":"Th\u1eddi gian gi\u1eef xe c\xf2n l\u1ea1i:","note-content6":"\u0110\u1eb7t c\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef xe v\xe0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n","note-shk":"C\xf3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn nhi\u1ec1u file s\u1ed5 h\u1ed9 kh\u1ea9u c\xf9ng l\xfac","note":"L\u01b0u \xfd:","content_note":["Nh\u1edb chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd v\xe0 t\xe0i s\u1ea3n \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ecdc th\u1ebf ch\u1ea5p theo y\xeau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ec7c thu\xea xe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i.","\u0110\u1ecdc k\u1ef9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\xea xe v\xe0 bi\xean b\u1ea3n b\xe0n giao xe c\u1ee7a B\xean cho thu\xea xe.","Ki\u1ec3m tra k\u1ef9 ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t, n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t v\xe0 m\xe1y m\xf3c trong qu\xe1 tr\xecnh nh\u1eadn xe.","Khi xe \u0111ang v\u1eadn h\xe0nh, th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\xean \u0111\u1ec3 \xfd \u0111\xe8n b\xe1o hi\u1ec7u tr\xean b\u1ea3ng t\xe1p l\xf4, n\u1ebfu th\u1ea5y \u0111\xe8n b\xe1o s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1, ho\u1eb7c xe c\xf3 hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\xe1c th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng xe ki\u1ec3m tra v\xe0 g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i b\xe1o ngay cho B\xean cho thu\xea xe \u0111\u1ec3 c\xf3 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3. Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p t\u1ef1 \xfd x\u1eed l\xfd ho\u1eb7c mang xe \u0111i s\u1eeda m\xe0 kh\xf4ng th\xf4ng b\xe1o ho\u1eb7c ch\u01b0a c\xf3 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \xfd c\u1ee7a B\xean cho thu\xea, th\xec s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu ho\xe0n to\xe0n tr\xe1ch nhi\u1ec7m.","Nghi\xeam t\xfac ch\u1ea5p h\xe0nh lu\u1eadt giao th\xf4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ed9. T\u1ef1 ch\u1ecbu tr\xe1ch nhi\u1ec7m d\xe2n s\u1ef1, h\xecnh s\u1ef1 trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian thu\xea xe. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p vi ph\u1ea1m lu\u1eadt giao th\xf4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ed9 v\xe0 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t ngu\u1ed9i, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu ho\xe0n to\xe0n tr\xe1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3n ph\xed ph\u1ea1t ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed9p v\u1edbi c\u01a1 quan ph\xe1p lu\u1eadt.","Chi ph\xed thu\xea xe kh\xf4ng bao g\u1ed3m c\xe1c chi ph\xed t\xe0i x\u1ebf, x\u0103ng d\u1ea7u, c\u1ea7u ph\xe0, b\u1ebfn b\xe3i,\u2026 trong qu\xe1 tr\xecnh thu\xea xe."],"content_note_motor":{"l1":"- Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\xe1c lo\u1ea1i gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho vi\u1ec7c thu\xea xe: CMND, B\u1eb1ng l\xe1i xe","l2":"- Ch\u1ecdn lo\u1ea1i xe (xe s\u1ed1, xe tay ga, xe c\xf4n) ph\xf9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecba h\xecnh v\xe0 th\xf3i quen.","l3":"- Ki\u1ec3m tra k\u1ef9 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng xe tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi thu\xea: b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec1, xi nhanh, c\xf2i, g\u01b0\u01a1ng, phanh ch\xe2n, phanh tay, c\u1ed5 xe..","l4":"- \u0110\u1ecdc k\u1ef9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\xea xe v\xe0 c\xe1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ph\u1ee5 tr\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 s\u1ed1 km gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n, qu\xe1 th\u1eddi gian thu\xea xe\u2026"}},"customer":{"title":"TH\xd4NG TIN KH\xc1CH H\xc0NG","fullname":"H\u1ecd v\xe0 t\xean","phone":"S\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i","email":"Email","address":"\u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn xe","btn":"Ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda"},"vehicle":{"title":"Chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u1eb7t xe","status":"Tr\u1ea1ng th\xe1i","payment":"Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c thanh to\xe1n","code":"M\xe3 \u0111\u1eb7t xe","type":"Lo\u1ea1i xe","form":"H\xecnh th\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn xe","time":"Th\u1eddi gian","btn":"Ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda","value":"Gi\xe1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t xe","amount":"S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n thanh to\xe1n","equals":"Ho\u1eb7c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng"}},"select_carriage":{"vehicle":{"btn_detail":"Chi ti\u1ebft","note1":"Gi\xe1 t\xednh theo ng\xe0y","note2":"Gi\xe1 ch\u01b0a bao g\u1ed3m ph\xed giao xe","unit":"VN\u0110","day":"ng\xe0y","note3":"(*) ng\xe0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\xednh t\u1eeb 7h-19h","note4":"Chungxe \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t","note5":"Chungxe \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t lo\u1ea1i xe n\xe0y d\u1ef1a tr\xean nhu c\u1ea7u th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\xf9ng !","text_not_load_more":"Kh\xf4ng c\xf2n xe. B\u1ea1n c\xf3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n l\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 x